Package com.google.appinventor.buildserver

Classes to build APKs for App Inventor projects.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
BuildServer Top level class for exposing the building of App Inventor APK files as a RESTful web service.
Compiler Main entry point for the YAIL compiler.
Execution Utility class for command execution and I/O redirection.
FormPropertiesAnalyzer Methods for analyzing the contents of a Young Android Form file.
Main Main entry point for the command line version of the YAIL compiler.
PathUtil Constants and utility methods related to storage.
Project This class gives access to Young Android project files.
Project.SourceDescriptor Representation of a source file containing its name and file location.
ProjectBuilder Provides support for building Young Android projects.
Result Class used to report results of an external call or remote process.
Signatures Helper methods to deal with type names and signatures.
YoungAndroidConstants Constants related to Young Android projects and files.
